  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC083">
          <l>vēṟṟumaip poruḷai virikkuṅ kālai</l>
	<l>yīṟṟuniṉ ṟiyalun tokaivayiṟ pirintu</l>
	<l>pallā ṟākap poruḷpuṇarn ticaikku</l>
	<l>mellāc collu muriya veṉpa.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/156/mode/1up">156</ref>.</p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Ilam-cit1">
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n89/mode/1up">86</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n90/mode/1up">87</ref>.</p>
      <p>i- ḷ. vēṟṟumaittokaiyai virikkumiṭattu, vēṟṟumaiyēyaṉṟi, aṉmoḻittokaiyai virippuḻip pallāṟṟāṉ aṉmoḻipporuḷoṭu puṇarntu varum ellāccollum, virikkappaṭum. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>urupu tokap poruṇiṟṟaliṉ, vēṟṟumaittokaiyai vēṟṟumaipporuḷeṉṟār. tokaiyai vēṟṟumaipporuḷeṉṟum, poruḷeṉṟum, yāṇṭumāḷpa.</p> 
<p>aṉmoḻittokai paṇputtokai mutalākiya tokai iṟuti niṉṟiyaṟaliṉ, īṟṟuniṉṟiyaluntokaiyeṉṟār.</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit1">
<l>tāḻkuḻal,</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit2">
<l>poṟṟoṭi,</l> 
</lg>
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit3">
<l>maṭkāraṇam</l> 
</lg>
<p>eṉṉum aṉmoḻittokaikaḷai virippuḻi, tāḻkuḻalaiyuṭaiyāḷ, poṟṟoṭiyaiyaṇintāḷ, maṇṇākiya kāraṇattāṉiyaṉṟatu eṉa varum uṭaimaiyum, aṇitalum, iyaṟalum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit4">
<l>karuṅkuḻaṟpētai,</l> 
</lg>
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit5">
<l>poṟṟoṭiyarivai,</l> 
</lg>
<lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit6">
<l>maṭkuṭam</l> 
</lg>
<p>eṉṉum vēṟṟumaittokaikaḷai virippuḻiyum, karuṅkuḻalaiyuṭaiya pētai, poṟṟoṭiyaiyaṇintavarivai, maṇṇāṉiyaṉṟa kuṭam eṉa vantavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.</p>
<p>poruḷpuṇarnticaikkumeṉavē, irutokaikkaṇṇum, oruvāypāṭṭāṉaṉṟip poruḷ citaiyāmaluṇarttutaṟkēṟṟa vāypāṭellāvaṟṟāṉum, varumeṉpatām. avvāṟātal mēṟkāṭṭappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟuṭkaṇṭukoḷka.</p>
<p>aṉmoḻittokaiyiṟ coṟpeytu virittal yāṇṭup peṟṟāmeṉiṉ;- atuvum anuvātamukattāṉ īṇṭē peṟṟāmeṉka. peṟavē, iraṇṭutokaiyum virippuḻi varum vēṟupāṭu kūṟiyavāṟām.</p>
<p>itaṉai</p> 
  <lg xml:id="TolC083-Cena-cit7">
  <l>"vēṟṟumait tokaiyē yuvamait tokaiyē"</l> 
  </lg>
<p>eṉṉuñcūttirattiṉ piṉ vaikkaveṉiṉ;- atuvumuṟaiyāyiṉum, iṉi varuñcūttiraṅkaḷāṉ vēṟṟumaittokai viripaṟṟiya mayakkamuṇarttutalāṉ, āṇṭuppaṭumuṟaimaiyuṇarttutal īṇṭumiyaipuṭaitteṉka.</p>
<p>uraiyāciriyar iraṇṭucūttiramāka aṟuttu āciriyarmatavikaṟpaṅkūṟit tammatamituveṉpatu pōtara oṉṟākavuraippārumuḷareṉṟār. iraṇṭāy oṉṟāyavaḻip piṟituraiyiṉmaiyiṉ, uraiyāciriyarkaruttituvēyām.	(22)</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena-cit1">
      </lg>
    </body>
